7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Copysmith and QuillBot share a solid foundation of core features including Short Form, Tone Control, Multilingual. Where Copysmith pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Templates and Api Access and Team Collaboration, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, QuillBot uniquely offers Plagiarism Check and Browser Extension, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Copysmith holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while QuillBot scores 7/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, QuillBot comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Copysmith begins at $19/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Copysmith's free tier and QuillBot's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
